$description = $config['content.description'] ?? 'Everything you need to know about playing poker at PokerArena. Can\'t find your answer? Contact our 24/7 support team.';

$faqRaw = $config['faq.items'] ?? "Is online poker legal on PokerArena?|PokerArena operates under strict licensing and regulatory frameworks. We hold licenses from recognized gaming authorities and comply with all applicable laws. Players must verify that online poker is permitted in their jurisdiction before playing.\nHow do deposits and withdrawals work?|We support a wide range of payment methods including credit/debit cards, e-wallets, bank transfers, and cryptocurrency. Deposits are instant, and withdrawals are processed within 24 hours. VIP members enjoy priority processing.\nWhat poker games are available?|We offer Texas Hold'em (NL, PL, FL), Omaha (NL, PL), Omaha Hi-Lo, Sit & Go tournaments, Multi-Table Tournaments (MTT), and special event tournaments. Stakes range from micro to high-roller tables.\nHow are the cards shuffled?|Our Random Number Generator (RNG) is independently certified by GLI and eCOGRA. Every deal is provably fair and uses cryptographic-grade randomness to ensure complete integrity.\nHow do I withdraw my winnings?|Navigate to the Cashier section, select your preferred withdrawal method, enter the amount, and confirm. Standard withdrawals process within 24 hours. E-wallet withdrawals are typically instant.\nDo you offer tournaments?|Yes! We run thousands of tournaments daily, from freerolls to million-dollar guaranteed events. Our tournament schedule includes daily, weekly, and seasonal series with buy-ins starting from $0.01.";

$faqs = [];
foreach (preg_split('/[\r\n]+/', $faqRaw) as $line) {
    $line = trim($line);
    if (empty($line)) continue;
    $parts = explode('|', $line, 2);
    if (!empty(trim($parts[0] ?? ''))) {
        $faqs[] = ['question' => trim($parts[0]), 'answer' => trim($parts[1] ?? '')];
    }
}

$instanceId = 'pa-faq-' . uniqid();
